==English==

===Noun===
'''polygordius'''
# {{zoology}} A genus of [[marine]] [[annelid]]s, believed to be an [[ancient]] or [[ancestral]] type. It is remarkable for its simplicity of structure and want of [[parapodia]]. It is the type of the order [[Archiannelida]], or [[Gymnotoma]].

